high_descs: Go straight then make a right and go around the bed. Turn left and face the bed
Pick up the cell phone on the bed that is close to the computer.
Turn around and go straight to the desk.
Put the cell phone on the desk horizontally.
Turn left and walk to the bed. At the bed make a left and go around to the other side of the bed.
Pick up the other cell phone on the bed.
Turn to the left walk forward turn left again. Turn right and walk to the desk.
Set the cell phone down horizontally on the right side of the other cell phone.
anns.task_desc: Move two cell phones from the bed to the desk.

high_descs: Turn right towards the shelves and then turn left towards the middle of the bed to your left.
Pick up the cellphone on the bed.
Turn around and head towards the desk.
Place the phone on the desk in front of the chair.
Turn around and head towards the bed with the blue cover.
Pick up the cellphone from the bed.
Turn left towards the edge of the bed, turn left at the book shelves, and then turn right towards the desk.
Place the cellphone to the right of the other cellphone on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Place the two cellphones from the beds on the desk.

high_descs: Walk around the end of the bed and approach the side of it where you see a red phone.
Pick up the red phone from the bed.
Turn left and walk to the desk and stand behind the office chair.
Set the phone on the desk.
Turn around and walk back toward the bed. Go around the first bed and turn right to walk between them and approach the side of the second bed.
Pick up the phone from the bed.
Turn to the left and walk back to the desk with the chair.
place the second phone on the desk next to the first phone.
anns.task_desc: Collect each cell phone and put them on the desk.
